        <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Why Choose This Salary Sacrifice Calculator?</h3>

        <p class="mb-4">
          Unlike generic pension calculators that ignore the National Insurance dimension, this tool correctly models the <strong>full tax treatment</strong> of both standard and salary sacrifice contributions. It accounts for employee NI savings (8% or 2%), employer NI savings (15%), and the potential employer pass-on that can boost your pension by an additional 15%. It also models the <strong>compound growth</strong> of these savings over your full working career, showing you the real difference salary sacrifice makes to your retirement pot.
        </p>

