          The calculator supports all three UK income tax bands (basic, higher, and additional), flexible employee and employer contribution percentages, employer NI pass-on toggling, and customisable growth rate and investment horizon assumptions. The interactive Chart.js chart shows the year-by-year projected pot growth for both scenarios, and the side-by-side comparison cards make it easy to see exactly how much more you accumulate with salary sacrifice.
